title: National Parks of New York Harbor: Photo Gallery
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Photo Gallery              Photo Gallery                    Media quality images of National Parks of New York Harbor   61 Photos  Each image is a minimum size of 2 MB. All images are taken by NPS employees or volunteers and are therefore in the public domain, so they may be used by anyone. We ask that you credit the photos as NPS PHOTO.
